{"type":"message","id":"4e03b795","parentId":"77420ae0","timestamp":"2026-04-15T04:13:00.302Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me compare current state vs last heartbeat state.\n\n**Last heartbeat state (03:22 UTC):**\n- Active: QLHV 5p cron ✅, DTLX 5p cron ✅, Agent Status cron ✅\n- Idle: QLHV group ✅, Lead direct ✅\n- Failed: DTLX group ❌\n- Orphans: ac986a8d, b653a6c0\n\n**Current state (04:12 UTC):**\n\nActive sessions:\n1. QLHV 5p cron ✅ (still running)\n2. DTLX 5p cron ✅ (still running)\n\n\n3. Agent Status cron ✅ — it shows as running in the sessions list, though it was aborted at 03:09:34 UTC and has been cycling through abort instances since then\n\nIdle sessions:\n1. QLHV group ✅ (last activity ~04:04 UTC)\n2. Lead direct ✅ (last activity ~03:51 UTC)\n\nFailed sessions:\n1. DTLX group ❌ (still failed since 03:16 UTC)\n\nOrphaned crons: Still present (ac986a8d, b653a6c0)\n\nNow I need to update the heartbeat state to reflect the current time of 04:12 UTC and send a report.\n\nLooking at the Agent Status cron, it's still running with the same session ID from before, but I'm noticing a discrepancy—the previous report at 04:02 UTC marked it as \"no longer active\" and the DTLX report flagged it as absent, yet the sessions list shows it as running. This suggests the cron might be stuck in an abort loop or the status is out of sync with what's actually happening.\n\nComparing the heartbeat state at 03:22 UTC against the current state at 04:12 UTC, the main changes are the Lead direct session spawning 6 new children and the QLHV group becoming active around 04:04 UTC. The Agent Status cron remains in its problematic state, and the DTLX group is still failing.\n\nSince there's a new message queued in the Lead direct session from the user asking about hiding configuration references and SOUL files, I should update the heartbeat state and generate a report rather than staying silent. Let me compose and send the report now, then save the updated state.","thinkingSignature":"7a7663476f32c42a8069a6577fe418b68b6d5decceef9ac79bdb54a435cdd50d"},{"type":"text","text":"Change detected. Compiling and sending report.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fs1kkm43ercq_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"memory/heartbeat-state.json","content":"{\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-15T04:12:00Z\",\n  \"activeSessions\": [\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\",\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e\"\n  ],\n  \"idleSessions\": [\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258\",\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\"\n  ],\n  \"failedSessions\": [\n    \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5168104492\"\n  ],\n  \"orphanedCrons\": [\n    \"cron:ac986a8d-2425-40c7-835b-ed9b101b0bff\",\n    \"cron:b653a6c0-143b-4b53-a242-034bc5fd9fca\"\n  ],\n  \"lastReportSent\": \"2026-04-15T04:12:00Z\",\n  \"lastReportGroup\": \"-5163901258\",\n  \"degradedReason\": \"DTLX Telegram group FAILED (500: providerSpecificData)\",\n  \"notes\": \"QLHV group reactivated at ~04:04 UTC. Lead direct has queued message from ~03:51 UTC.\"\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":23897,"output":868,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":417,"totalTokens":39126,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776226362272,"responseId":"062e433b0cc11637c5a053abd8b48ae0"}}
